874
00:53:55,189 --> 00:53:56,560
Sejak kapan kamu tahu?

875
00:53:56,630 --> 00:53:57,759
Sudah lama.

876
00:54:00,699 --> 00:54:01,769
Ibu.

877
00:54:04,800 --> 00:54:06,600
Jangan tinggalkan aku.

878
